title: Philippines Building Permits
description: Building Permits in Philippines decreased to 37270 in the first quarter of 2022 from 39513 in the fourth quarter of 2021. Building Permits in Philippines averaged 29071.14  from 2001 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 45578  in the third quarter of 2018 and a record low of 16129  in the third quarter of 2001. This page provides - Philippines Building Permits- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
